{"tid":248792,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"264R一討","createTime":"2017-05-18T23:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T23:24:57.000Z","uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44def3cea3240c8adea8118a57ebbf6e5d3ea9d4","tid":248792,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T23:24:57.000Z","msg":"我見過好多人屌264R收費高<br />\n呢樣野的確冇得坳, 佢收成$15.8 (64K先$8.4, 車又多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 仲貴過我東鐵去上水轉276/276P (4.3+9.2=13.5)<br />\n但係佢速度上真係好吸引<br />\n大埔中心出發, 35-40分鐘到元朗, 冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (東鐵轉276/276P加埋K12就兩回事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n所以264R其實唔係冇得做, 不過好心減下價啦, 我搭271出到尖沙咀都係$11.1咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實64K大埔去元朗其非想像中咁慢, 去大埔墟的確東鐵轉276/276P冇得輸, 但去太和嘅話只係快64K 10-15分鐘, 去大埔中心更有機會打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去太和同大埔中心比多果$5.1抵唔抵, 自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}